150 U.S. 84 (1893)

WELLS
v.
GOODNOW'S ADMINISTRATOR.

No. 160.

Supreme Court of United States.

Submitted October 10, 1893.
Decided October 16, 1893.
ERROR TO THE SUPREME COURT OF THE STATE OF IOWA.

Mr. George Crane for the motion.

Mr. C.H. Gatch and Mr. William Connor opposing.

THE CHIEF JUSTICE:

The writ of error is dismissed for the want of jurisdiction upon the authority of Chapman v. Goodnow, 123 U.S. 540.
